<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Organization</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset styles to ensure consistency across email clients */
    body, body * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* Set a background color for the email */
    body {
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    }

    /* Container to center the email content */
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    /* Header styles */
    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* Main content styles */
    .content {
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #555555;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Footer styles */
    footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #777777;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
    }

    footer p {
      margin: 0;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #3498db;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer img {
      max-width: 50%;
      height: auto;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>Fittonia Technologies Pvt. Ltd.</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear Admin,</p>
      <br>

      <p>A new candidate has applied for the ROR back-end role at Fittonia Technologies. Here are the details:</p>
      <br>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%= @candidate.first_name %> <%= @candidate.last_name %></li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @candidate.email %></li>
        <li><strong>Phone Number:</strong> <%= @candidate.phone_number %></li>
        <li><strong>Address:</strong> <%= @candidate.address %></li>
        <li><strong>Gender:</strong> <%= @candidate.gender %></li>
        <li><strong>Education:</strong> <%= @candidate.education %></li>
        <li><strong>Skills:</strong> <%= @candidate.skill.join(', ') %></li>
        <li><strong>Experience:</strong> <%= @candidate.experiance %></li>
        <!-- Add any other relevant details here -->
      </ul>
      <br>

      <p>Please review the application and take the necessary actions.</p>

      <br>
      <p>Best regards,<br>Fittonia Technologies HR Team</p>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <p>Contact HR Department:</p>
      <p>Email: hr@ftpls.com</p>
      <p>Phone: +91 97556 90367</p>
      <p>Visit our website: <a href="https://ftpls.com" target="_blank">www.ftpls.com</a></p>
      <img src="https://admin.ftpls.com/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBOdz09IiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--fe31acdb7e3b4339ea47b07fa84d24af57f8d6d0/logo2x-d1fd207ffc97e14b77791471e2eefa7d3a2e168920bdb982fd26262b5cec6510.png" alt="HR Department Image">
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

